Wallet > Advisory Page

User Story

User should be navigated to an advisory page displaying

Available funds

Forecasted expenses for the month.

Forecasted income for the month.

Investment advice.

Technical Task

Task 1: Develop screen for advisory page where user can view the Forecasted expense, Forecasted income and available cash.

Task 2 : Data should be taken from the DB file.

Task 3 : Integrating screen with back end services

Task 4: Unit Testing.

